  "text": "Where did the second density beings get physical vehicles of third density type to incarnate into I am wrong? There were among those upon this second density plane, those forms which, when exposed to third density vibrations, became the third density, as you would call a sound vibration, human entities. That is, there was a loss of the body hair, as you call it, the clothing of the body to protect it, the a changing of the structure of the a neck, a jaw, and a forehead in order to allow the easier vocalization and the larger cranial development characteristic of third density needs. This was a normal transfiguration.",
